to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"D-Day veterans must have laughed.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"D-Day veterans\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A nation that cannot stop 90,000 migrants from reaching the UK had no trouble escorting 84 ships and just 6,500 athletes down the Seine.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3059, \"end\": 3061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999897072173028, \"rank\": 1.0012612847500282e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.131910717076383e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A nation\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"90,000 migrants\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"no trouble\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"84 ships\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"just 6,500 athletes\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So France finally got the Games it so desperately wanted in 2012.\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.5921990046733622, \"rank\": 0.33281741270078385, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time there wasn't a piece of 'fromage and pain' in sight - just lots of 'pain', and rain.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"fromage\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3245}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"just lots\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After an hour the cameramen could not be bothered to wipe the rain off their lens, and who could blame them?\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3311}, {\"ngram\": \"the cameramen\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"their lens\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST OPINION: The guests were nearly all US celebrities, and a haunted-looking Rafael Nadal - all symbolic of the fact France has virtually no international profile these days.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8859476362230702, \"rank\": 0.128539826507688, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3530, \"end\": 3536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.5921990046733622, \"rank\": 0.33281741270078385, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LATEST OPINION\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"The guests\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"all symbolic\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"virtually no international profile\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French attempts to ape modernity always fail, not least because France has a Net Zero impact on world culture: its attempt at modern dance with peculiar costumes convinced no one.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3589, \"end\": 3595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9919001120626367, \"rank\": 0.00434526403187337, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.5921990046733622, \"rank\": 0.33281741270078385, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"modernity\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3621}, {\"ngram\": \"a Net Zero impact\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"world culture\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"its attempt\", \"from\": 3700, \"to\": 3711}, {\"ngram\": \"modern dance\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3727}, {\"ngram\": \"peculiar costumes\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The failure of large TV screens exemplified France's near-zero ability to create any IT or internet companies of note.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3814, \"end\": 3820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.5921990046733622, \"rank\": 0.33281741270078385, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.